  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to access to the abdominal cavity using different incision-types
      within the umbilical area.

      Effects of different incisions on scarring and on the umbilical form will be investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
